ttp_template:
<group name="nexthop_interface">
  nexthop {{NEXTHOP}} {{INTERFACE | ORPHRASE}}
</group>
<group name="prefix_epoch_sharing">
{{PREFIX}}, epoch {{EPOCH}}, per-{{SHARING | ORPHRASE}}
</group>
cli_content:
0.0.0.0/0, epoch 2, per-destination sharing
  adjacency: 0.0.0.0
  nexthop 192.168.1.1 GigabitEthernet0/1
  packets 123, bytes 45678

192.168.1.0/24, epoch 2, per-destination sharing
  adjacency: 192.168.1.0
  nexthop 10.0.0.1 GigabitEthernet0/2
  packets 78, bytes 12345
  
2001:db8::/32, epoch 2, per-flow

textfsm_template:
Value PREFIX (\S+)
Value EPOCH (\d+)
Value SHARING (\S+)
Value ADJACENCY (\S+)
Value NEXTHOP (\S+)
Value INTERFACE (\S+)
Value PACKETS (\d+)
Value BYTES (\d+)

Start
  ^\s*${PREFIX},\s*epoch\s*${EPOCH},\s*per-${SHARING}\s*$$
  ^\s*adjacency:\s*${ADJACENCY}\s*$$
  ^\s*nexthop\s*${NEXTHOP}\s*${INTERFACE}\s*$$
  ^\s*packets\s*${PACKETS},\s*bytes\s*${BYTES}\s*$$ -> Record
